<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Poliksena Blog</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
          font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          background: url("http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-c-Z0i16rV6U/VI2Q3_p3woI/AAAAAAAABEs/P7dyrMzdxUk/s1600/symphony-1.png");
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
        }
        header {
          width: 100%;
          text-align: center;
          background-color: #FFFFFF;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 20px;
          font-family: Trattatello ;
          font-size: 40px;
        }
        #menu{
          width: 100%;
          height: 40px;
          background-color: #FFFFFF;
          text-align: center;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 10px;
        }
        #menu a{
          margin-right: 10px;
        }
        #container {
          width: 760px;
          margin: 0 auto;
        }
        a, a:visited {
          text-decoration: none;
          color: #B00100;
        }
        a:hover {
          font-weight: bold;
        }
        .post {
          background-color: #FFFFFF;
          width: 100%;
          margin: 15px 0;
          padding: 40px;
          text-align: justify;
          box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .post h1{
          text-align: center;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          font-family: Inconsolata, serif;
          padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .post h2{
          text-align: left;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          font-family: Mishafi, serif;
        }
        .post h4{
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 14px;

        }
        .szczegolyPosta {
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 14px;
          font-weight: bold;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: #8d8d8d;

        }
        .comment {
          border-style: groove ridge inset outset;
          padding: 0 15px 15px 15px;
          font-size: 14px;
          font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          margin: 20px 20px 0px 20px;
        }
        .comment h1{
          text-transform: uppercase;
          display: inline;
          font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          font-size: 12px;
        }
        .comment h2{
          font-size: 12px;
          font-family: "Arial Narrow", sans-serif;
          display: inline;
          color: #999999;
        }
        .przyciski{
          text-transform: uppercase;
          text-align: right;
          font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          font-size: 12px;
          padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;
        }
        footer{
          background-color: #2E2F30;
          color: white;
          margin: 0;
          width: 100%;
          clear: both;
          text-align: center;
          padding: 10px;
        }
        .parametryPosta{
          color: #999999;
          text-align: left;
          font-size: 14px;
          font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, Sans-Serif;
        }
        #pasekDolny{
          font-family: Calibri, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          background: url("http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-TnrWMh-lg_A/VI2RPNyXcfI/AAAAAAAABE0/LmXEFTuLrjE/s1600/header_pattern.jpg");
          width: 100%;
          padding: 0;
          margin: auto;
        }
        .trescNaPaskuDolnym{
          float: left;
          width: 200px;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0 0 0 20px;
          text-align: justify;
        }
        #containerPaskaDolnego{
          width: 900px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 0;
          color: white;

        }
        .trescNaPaskuDolnym h1{
          color: #DADADA;
          font-size: 20px;
          font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, Sans-Serif;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF;
          font-weight: bold;
        }
        #tag{
          text-align: center;
          background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
          border: 1px ridge grey;
          margin-top: 40px;
          font-size: 30px;
          font-family: "Arial Narrow";
          color: #999999;
          padding: 15px;
        }

    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
      <header>
        <h1>Poliksena Blog</h1>
      </header>
      <div id="menu">
          <%= link_to 'Strona główna', root_path %>
          <%= link_to 'Artykuły', articles_path %>
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <%= link_to 'Wyloguj', destroy_user_session_path %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to 'Logowanie', new_user_session_path %>
          <% end %>
      </div>
    <div id="container">
      <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
      <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
      <%= yield %>
    </div>
    <div id="pasekDolny">
      <div id="containerPaskaDolnego">
        <div class="trescNaPaskuDolnym">
          <h1>About Author </h1>
          <img src="https://media3.giphy.com/media/JIX9t2j0ZTN9S/200_s.gif">
          <p>Student informatyki</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trescNaPaskuDolnym">
          <h1>Tagi</h1>
          <p><%= render template: "tags/index" %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="trescNaPaskuDolnym">
          <h1>Cos tu bedzie</h1>
          <p>Duis viverra laoreet risus, a hendrerit lorem cursus vel. Proin feugiat odio leo, vel venenatis magna egestas vel. Nam a euismod augue, sed aliquam nisl.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trescNaPaskuDolnym">
          <h1>Nowy artykuł</h1>
          <p>Aby stworzyć nowy artykuł kliknij w link poniżej</p>
          <p><%= link_to 'New article', new_article_path %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br style="clear: left;">
    </div>
    <footer>2017 Poliksena Blog</footer>
  </body>
</html>
